cat << EOF
XdTV is a software that allows you to watch TV. It interacts with AleVT
for Teletext and Nxtvepg for NextView. It uses the video4linux API. It can
use deinterlacing filters and record video files with the ffmpeg, xvid,
and divx codecs.
EOF
